message: Prioritize the Growth Serum! Use it first on individual medium or large ingredients to raise their value. The most successful strategy is to then use the Growth Serum multiple times on positively valued, combined items that have 2-3 components. Avoid the Mutation Catalyst; it consistently leads to negative values. Be very cautious when combining more than 3 items, especially if 'large' animals are involved; 'overcomplicated' items tend to be very bad. Submit your score when you have a good value and further actions seem risky.
